Create a new Anaconda Environment for the analysis project, running the code below in cmd;
          conda create --name cryptocurrency_analysis python=3
To activate the environment run in cmd;
          activate cryptocurerncy-analysis 
To install the following required dependencies in your environment run in cmd;
          conda install numpy pandas nb_conda jupyter plotly quandl
To start a notebook run in cmd;
          jupyter notebook
The following link will open your notebookm in your browser of choice
          http://localhost:8888/
Using the Kernel that previously set up
          Python [conda env:cryptocurrency-analysis]

